		</introduction>
		<task>
			<statement>
				<p>
					What was the teen pregnancy rate in 2003?
				</p>
			</statement>
		</task>
		<task>
			<statement>
				<p>
					Did the teen pregnancy rate increase or decrease from 2003 to 2004?
				</p>
			</statement>
		</task>
		<task>
			<statement>
				<p>
					While the teen pregnancy rate has generally decreased, 
					from 2001 to 2002 it actually increased. 
					Were there other times when it increased?
				</p>
			</statement>
		</task>
		<task>
			<statement>
				<p>
					When did the teen pregnancy rate first fall below 60 pregnancies per thousand teens?
				</p>
			</statement>
		</task>
		<task>
			<statement>
				<p>
					How fast was the teen pregnancy rate dropping on average per year from 2002 to 2005? 
					How does that compare to 2006 to 2009?
				</p>
			</statement>
		</task>
		
	</exercise>
</page>

